{"type":null,"faqId":10848,"title":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）  邮箱设置","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">添加</span><span>Email</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">帐户</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入</span> <b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">账户</span><span> &gt; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">添加账户</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。选择<b>电子邮件</b>添加</span><span>Email</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">账户，选择<b>公司</b>添加</span><span>Exchange</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">账户。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31953\" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<b><span>-- </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手动设置：</span><span></span></b> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">账户设置界面</span><span> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">输入账号和密码。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击手动设置。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击</span><span>POP3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，进入接收服务器设置界面。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-s